item.title: Fall 2015 Event Scheduling - Event Processing Begins
item.description: FMS begins processing fall event requests.  All requests received prior to this date are processed first.  All requests received today and later are not processed until the queued requests are completed.  Due to high volume, please allow up to two weeks for event confirmation.
